  "title": "Send click events in vue 3 - TypeError: window.aa is not a function",
  "body": "### 🐛 Current behavior\n\nI am trying to follow this guide to send click events in vue 3: \r\nhttps://www.algolia.com/doc/guides/building-search-ui/events/vue/\r\n\r\nWhen calling `window.aa(\"setUserToken\", \"test-user-123\")` to set user token, I get the error:\r\n\r\n`TypeError: window.aa is not a function`\r\n\r\nHow to configure this using vue 3 ?\n\n### 🔍 Steps to reproduce\n\n- create a new vue project\r\n- follow the steps in https://www.algolia.com/doc/guides/building-search-ui/events/vue/\r\n\n\n### Live reproduction\n\nh\n\n### 💭 Expected behavior\n\nUser token should be set. \n\n### Package version\n\n\"vue-instantsearch\": \"^4.17.5\", \"vue\": \"^3.0.0\",\n\n### Operating system\n\nwindows\n\n### Browser\n\n_No response_\n\n### Code of Conduct\n\n- [X] I agree to follow this project's Code of Conduct",
